msgstr ""
"&kmenuedit; pagalba galite redaguoti visus &kde; programų paleidimo meniu: "
"&kickoff;, klasikinį bei Lancelot."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmenuedit; can be started either by &RMB; clicking the application launcher "
"button on the panel and choosing <guimenuitem>Edit Applications...</"
"guimenuitem>, or by typing <userinput>kmenuedit</userinput> in the &krunner; "
"line."
msgstr ""
"&kmenuedit; galite paleisti arba spausdami <mousebutton>dešinįjį</"
"mousebutton> pelės mygtuką ant programų paleidimo mygtuko ir pasirinkdami "
"punktą <guimenuitem>Redaguoti programas...</guimenuitem>, arba &krunner; "
"programoje įrašę <userinput>kmenuedit </userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kmenuedit; allows you to:"
msgstr "Su &kmenuedit; jūs galite:"

