#: index.docbook:327
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description:"
msgstr "Aprašymas:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:328
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The description will be displayed together with the name in the application "
"launcher. This is entirely optional."
msgstr ""
"Programos aprašymas bus irgi rodomas programų paleidimo meniu. Šis laukas "
"yra neprivalomas."

